data.eml:eml: An account on the Orthoptera from Siargao Island (Southeast Asia: Philippines: Mindanao)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tan, Ming Kai, Baroga-Barbecho, Jessica B., Yap, Sheryl A. (2019): An account on the Orthoptera from Siargao Island (Southeast Asia: Philippines: Mindanao). Zootaxa 4609 (1): 1-30, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4609.1.1
